            "content_html": "<p>Here is a list of online open access presentations which I gave for internal seminars, courses or conferences.</p>\n<h3>Presentations</h3>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/Reveal_Presentations/2019_02_21_RNA_club_Gurdon/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"padding: 5px;\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/2019_02_21_RNA_club_Gurdon.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2019_02_21_RNA_club_Gurdon-xs.png 300w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2019_02_21_RNA_club_Gurdon-sm.png 480w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2019_02_21_RNA_club_Gurdon-md.png 749w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2019_02_21_RNA_club_Gurdon-xl.png 1200w\"  alt=\"\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/Reveal_Presentations/2020_06_01_London_calling/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"padding: 5px;\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/2020_06_01_London_calling.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_01_London_calling-xs.png 300w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_01_London_calling-sm.png 480w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_01_London_calling-md.png 749w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_01_London_calling-xl.png 1200w\"  alt=\"\"></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/Reveal_Presentations/2020_01_23_Tea_talk_AL/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"padding: 5px;\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/2020_01_23_Tea_talk_AL.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Tea_talk_AL-xs.png 300w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Tea_talk_AL-sm.png 480w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Tea_talk_AL-md.png 749w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Tea_talk_AL-xl.png 1200w\"  alt=\"\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/Reveal_Presentations/2020_01_23_Good_enough_software_development_practices/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"padding: 5px;\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/2020_01_23_Good_enough_software_development_practices-3.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Good_enough_software_development_practices-3-xs.png 300w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Good_enough_software_development_practices-3-sm.png 480w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Good_enough_software_development_practices-3-md.png 749w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_01_23_Good_enough_software_development_practices-3-xl.png 1200w\"  alt=\"\"></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/Reveal_Presentations/2020_06_15_Birney_virtual_retreat/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" style=\"padding: 5px;\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/2020_06_15_Birney_virtual_retreat-2.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_15_Birney_virtual_retreat-2-xs.png 300w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_15_Birney_virtual_retreat-2-sm.png 480w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_15_Birney_virtual_retreat-2-md.png 749w ,https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/responsive/2020_06_15_Birney_virtual_retreat-2-xl.png 1200w\"  alt=\"\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"> </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Posters</h3>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/LC2020_Adrien_leger_poster.png\" data-size=\"4966x7021\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/LC2020_Adrien_leger_poster-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1272\"></a>\n<figcaption>London calling 2020: Differential CpG methylation analysis with pycoMeth</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/London_calling_Poster-2.png\" data-size=\"5000x7069\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/London_calling_Poster-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1272\"></a>\n<figcaption>London calling 2019: Signal level RNA modifications detection in eukaryotic non-coding RNAs with NanoCompore</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/London_calling_Poster-3.png\" data-size=\"5000x7069\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/London_calling_Poster-3-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1272\"></a>\n<figcaption>London calling 2018: Where's Wally? Finding RNA modifications with ONT direct-RNA Sequencing</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Poster_EMBO_BC.png\" data-size=\"3364x4756\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/13/gallery/Poster_EMBO_BC-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1272\"></a>\n<figcaption>EMBO gene therapy conference 2015: rAAV vector genome characterisation by NGS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>",
