            "content_html": "<h3 class=\"_2yYPPW47QxD4lFQTKpfpLQ\">Data Is Beautiful !</h3>\n<p>A selection of plots and infographics I generated for various research projects.</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper gallery-wrapper--wide\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/CGI_Finder.png\" data-size=\"1159x411\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/CGI_Finder-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"CpG plot\" width=\"900\" height=\"319\"></a>\n<figcaption>Plots CpGs islands identified with pycoMeth CpG finder. Not a new, but efficient</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/channels_activity.png\" data-size=\"1400x600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/channels_activity-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"pycoQC channel\" width=\"900\" height=\"386\"></a>\n<figcaption>Nanopore Flowcell channel activity plot. One of the unique plot generated with pycoQC.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/medaka_graph.png\" data-size=\"2294x506\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/medaka_graph-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Graph_example\" width=\"900\" height=\"199\"></a>\n<figcaption>Example section of HdrR/HNI/HSOK/MIKK pangenome graph assembly</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/pycoQC_align.png\" data-size=\"1048x513\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/pycoQC_align-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"pycoQC alignment\" width=\"900\" height=\"441\"></a>\n<figcaption>Alignment status flowchart from the HTML report generated by pycoQC</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/pycoMeth_CpG_ridegplot-2.png\" data-size=\"1376x946\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/pycoMeth_CpG_ridegplot-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"pycoMeth_ridgeplot\" width=\"900\" height=\"619\"></a>\n<figcaption>Differentially methylated CpG island ridgeplot generated by pycoMeth</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/pycoMeth_CpG_heatmap-2.png\" data-size=\"1515x935\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/pycoMeth_CpG_heatmap-2-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"pycoMeth_heatmap\" width=\"900\" height=\"555\"></a>\n<figcaption>Differentially methylated CpG island heatmap generated by pycoMeth</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/MEIS1.png\" data-size=\"2233x973\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/MEIS1-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Methylation_Meis1\" width=\"900\" height=\"392\"></a>\n<figcaption>Methylation profile of MEIS1 in human samples obtained with pycoMeth</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/1-s2.0-S2162253116300452-gr5_lrg.jpg\" data-size=\"3395x1957\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/1-s2.0-S2162253116300452-gr5_lrg-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"AAV-cov\" width=\"900\" height=\"519\"></a>\n<figcaption>Comparative sequencing depth along the rAAV vector plasmid and visualization of ITR/backbone junctions</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/7SK_nanocompore.png\" data-size=\"944x402\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/7SK_nanocompore-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"RN7SK-m6A\" width=\"900\" height=\"383\"></a>\n<figcaption>m6A RNA modification profile of RN7SK transcript obtained with NanoCompore</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/RNA_HDRR_21761679-1776422_igvbandage.png\" data-size=\"2859x2157\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/RNA_HDRR_21761679-1776422_igvbandage-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Graph_insertion\" width=\"900\" height=\"679\"></a>\n<figcaption>Alternative divergent path in medaka pangenome graph assembly</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/deletions.png\" data-size=\"2548x1180\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/deletions-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Graph_deletions\" width=\"900\" height=\"417\"></a>\n<figcaption>Example of deletions identified in in medaka pangenome graph assembly</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/insertions.png\" data-size=\"2432x1172\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/insertions-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"Graph_insertion with RNA-Seq profile\" width=\"900\" height=\"434\"></a>\n<figcaption>Alternative divergent segment including RNA-seq assembly path in medaka pangenome graph assembly</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/SARS_Cycle.png\" data-size=\"3781x2662\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://adrienleger.com/media/posts/8/gallery/SARS_Cycle-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"SARS-COV2 cycle\" width=\"900\" height=\"634\"></a>\n<figcaption>SARS-COV2 cycle infographics made with inkscape. It summarises dozens of paper in a graphical way.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<p> </p>",
